      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZINFANDEL EMMA (8) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 5.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 30.53. Outside box to overcome but goes well at this distance. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Can continue the winning form. CONQUEROR (1) was in the money last time at this track (30.92) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths second. Has already won two times from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. GALACTIC NEMESIS (2) has a strong overall record having 22 wins and 19 places from 55 starts including a last start success (30.90) over 530m at this track. Has a good record here including six wins. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. TODD KEEPING (7) hit the frame here last start and can sneak into the finish again.",
